---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const bookingUrl = 'https://calendar.app.google/rC9Kz37aZANXAUgt5';
---

<Base
  title="You're in. Let's talk"
  description="Thanks for telling Jonathan what's next for your agent. Book a free 15-minute call to map your next move."
>
  <div class="container next-page">
    <div class="book-hero panel">
      <p class="book-kicker">One Last Step &middot; Do This Now</p>
      <h1>Book your free 15-min call.</h1>

      <div class="book-cta-wrap">
        <a href={bookingUrl} class="book-cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="book-cta-main">Pick a time &rarr;</span>
          <span class="book-cta-sub">Free &middot; 15 min</span>
        </a>
        <p class="book-urgency">
          <span class="book-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Easiest while it's still fresh. Do it now
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="book-sub">
        You just told me where you want to take your agent. The fastest way to
        get there is 15 minutes with me, looking at your actual workflow. Bring
        the one task you'd most like off your plate.
      </p>

      <ul class="book-benefits">
        <li>A clear read on whether your workflow is worth automating</li>
        <li>The specific next step to build it, or an honest &ldquo;not yet,&rdquo; and why</li>
        <li>No pitch, no slides, just your work and a plan</li>
      </ul>

      <a href={bookingUrl} class="book-cta book-cta-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="book-cta-main">Book my free call &rarr;</span>
      </a>

      <p class="book-reassure">
        100% free &middot; 15 minutes &middot; no obligation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
